{"tid":1583553,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"過左921清潔日，我要連儂牆幫我翻身以下幾類文宣，每人印10張","createTime":"2019-09-20T16:00:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T17:03:43.000Z","uid":49753,"like":76,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"431d31bb5d12a18c1e127288053052c7e14bbdcc","tid":1583553,"uid":49753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T16:00:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">過左921清潔日，我要連儂牆幫我翻身以下幾類文宣，每人印10張</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>1. 歷史回顧</strong></span><br />\n將由69遊行開始，所有發生過既團結事件同埋悲傷事件，都詳盡簡單咁列哂俾人睇<br />\n可以既就由送中條例出現開始都需要<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>2. 追究案件</strong></span><br />\n612暴動決定，721唔見人，831事件，新屋嶺疑團，臥底冇犯法等等<br />\n一一將所有疑團同新發現證據貼哂出黎，我要所有地方都睇有咩要質疑既原因<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>3. 時代革命、願榮光歸香港</strong></span><br />\n請好好考慮製作/光復任何用口表達既和理非打氣活動，要叫既口號同要唱既歌就更加要好好宣傳<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>4. 更多和你X活動，重練春袋</strong></span><br />\n有好多和理非活動，濫暴機會極細，亦該不斷發掘同改良活動，過去成功過就要堅持<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>5. 未來活動+時間表</strong></span><br />\n連儂牆長期更新力度不足，所有人同我將活動翻身，85罷工罷左兩次啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>6. 美國法案、馬格尼茨基人權問責法</strong></span><br />\n美國既香港民主人權法案，同埋馬格尼茨基人權問責法，係香港人求生既必要法律知識，任何人都應該需要係連儂牆到，認識了解呢兩條分分鐘係救命草既法案<br />\n<br />\n<strong>7. 十一</strong><br />\n賀鄰國70大壽，大家可以表揚下佢地係民主同自由進程上，有咩風光偉蹟，知唔知咩係8964，文化大革命發生咩事，長春餓殍戰咩黎"},{"pid":"9bc90bf3f81ab127ac7e195b9a8baf6243d0da0c","tid":1583553,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T16:01:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑警藍絲必須還眼、斷手斷腳！！</span><br />\n9.21光復屯門+元朗站，9.22機場，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">9.29全球反赤納粹，10.1國殤全民黑衣</span></strong><br />\n<strong>831臥底警犬開真槍實彈鎮壓示威者！太子站恐襲！中聯辦葉虎！</strong><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">用twitter、reddit參與國際文宣\n跳閘/轉搭巴士\n全面批鬥警犬及其家屬\n㩒錢/換美金，經濟制裁中共\n全面杯葛tvb廣告商同藍絲企業！\n#antichinazi</code></pre>"},{"pid":"e4c5067576c918dee2f6f240199392d5b8a79455","tid":1583553,"uid":259973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T16:03:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"07e130cf9d1aa92a0f88b59100cd67ef59a05520","tid":1583553,"uid":77137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T16:06:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b5e8948e714024924d095862bdc96dd3bc30e26c","tid":1583553,"uid":49753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T16:06:29.000Z","msg":"7.1 <br />\n知唔知咩係大嗚大放?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09f6b0f7217580faf5eb7f92db201627829d6604","tid":1583553,"uid":49753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5e8948e714024924d095862bdc96dd3bc30e26c","tid":1583553,"uid":49753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T16:06:29.000Z","msg":"7.1 <br />\n知唔知咩係大嗚大放?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T16:07:57.000Z","msg":"大鳴大放"},{"pid":"002ea6e8695162b8702ff97beb829b10998cd5a6","tid":1583553,"uid":270956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T16:09:07.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8095a8da65fabd8004abcbe2071be4c6c5daf2e","tid":1583553,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T16:16:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">割蓆宣言 - 幫手翻譯, 做文宣圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/kMrteqX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/kMrteqX</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">[新行動]</span> [增加國際輿論] <span style=\"color: orange;\">推到林奠戴住豬嘴口罩, 頭盔對話</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1582650